metadata.name: World of Emotions
metadata.description:
Close your eyes, take a deep breath and sink into the world of emotions. Let yourself flow there. 

Model: Liza Sviridova.  
Photographed in Kaş, Turkey in June, 2022.

“World of Emotions” is the first piece of “Dozen”, a collection of 12 photos. For 12 months, one photo from the collection is released as 12 editions at 12:00pm (GMT) on the 12th of each month. Each photo is live by the end of the month. 

  Following this project for 12 months and collecting all 12 pieces, collectors own a unique 1/1 NFT as well as its signed metal print. At the end of the year, collectors who collect 6+ pieces have a signed and numbered fine art print. 

Every month, an edition is gifted to one lucky holder of Belong to Ocean by a raffle.
